E-commerce Product Price Prediction

A Machine Learning-based web application that predicts product prices using historical data.
This project demonstrates end-to-end development — from model building to deployment using a web interface.

Project Overview :-
This project uses Linear Regression to predict product prices based on historical datasets.
A lightweight Flask web app allows users to input product features and get predicted prices instantly.

Tech Stack :-
Machine Learning: Scikit-learn
Programming Language: Python
Backend: Flask
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Features :-
Predict product prices using trained ML model
Fast and lightweight Flask backend
User-friendly web interface

Machine Learning Model :-
Algorithm: Linear Regression
Library: Scikit-learn
Workflow:
Data preprocessing
Feature selection
Model training
Model evaluation
Model serialization using pickle

How It Works :-
User inputs product details in the web form
Data is sent to Flask backend
Model predicts the price
Predicted result is displayed on UI
